</div>
<div id="u-credit-00118-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/m-element" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2941964); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2941964&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180054" alt="M Element" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2941964)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/m-element" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2941964); return false;">M Element</a></span></p>
